'''伯納·霍根-豪'''爵士，[[女皇警察獎章|QPM]]（{{lang-en|Sir '''Bernard Hogan-Howe'''}}，{{bd|1957年|10月25日|||Hogan-Howe, Sir Bernard}}），是一名[[英國|英國]][[警官|警官]]，生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[雪菲爾|雪菲爾]]，於2011年起出任[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]{{Link-en|倫敦警察廳總監|Commissioner of Police of the Metropolis|總監}}。

霍根-豪於1979年起加入警隊，先後在[[南約克郡|南約克郡]]及[[默西塞德郡|默西塞德郡]]等地方警察部門服務過，持有[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]應用犯罪學文憑、[[牛津大學|牛津大學]][[法學碩士|法學碩士]]及[[雪菲爾大學|雪菲爾大學]][[工商管理碩士|工商管理碩士]][[學位|學位]]。原任警察廳總監{{Link-en|保羅·史蒂文生 (英國警官)|Paul Stephenson (police officer)|保羅·史蒂文生}}於2011年7月辭職後，霍根-豪於同年8月和另外3名人候選人同角逐有關職位<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14549497|title=Four in running to be next Met Police commissioner|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2011-08-17|accessdate=2012-01-04|archive-date=2011-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111205230228/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14549497|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年9月12日，霍根-豪通過[[內政大臣|內政大臣]]和[[倫敦市長|倫敦市長]]的面試、成功獲選為新一屆總監，在接受女皇任命後，獲[[首都警察監管局|首都警察監管局]]批准上任<ref name="appointment">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14888118 |title=Bernard Hogan-Howe new Metropolitan Police commissioner |publisher=BBC News |date=2011-09-12 |accessdate=2011-09-12 |archive-date=2011-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110912172829/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14888118 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年，霍根-豪因為在警界的服務表現，而被列入當年度的{{Link-en|2013年英國新年授勳名冊|2013 New Year Honours|新年授勳名冊}}，成為[[下級勳位爵士|下級勳位爵士]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1031058/new-year-honours-kate-bush-heads-arts-field|author=|title=New Year Honours: Kate Bush Heads Arts Field|publisher=[[Sky_News|Sky News]]|date=2012-12-28|accessdate=2012-12-29|archive-date=2013-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130101042216/http://news.sky.com/story/1031058/new-year-honours-kate-bush-heads-arts-field|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年2月22日卸任，繼任者克雷西達·迪克是英國首位女性警察廳總監。

==早年生涯==
霍根-豪於1957年出生於[[雪菲爾|雪菲爾]]，父親為伯納·豪（{{lang|en|Bernard Howe}}），但從小由母親單獨扶養，因此他透過{{Link-en|改名契|Deed of change of name}}將母姓「霍根」（{{lang|en|Hogan}}）加在父姓前。霍根-豪後來進入辛德屋學校（{{lang|en|Hinde House School}}）念完小學部和中學部，獲得[[普通教育高级程度证书|中等教育文憑]]，畢業之後赴[[英國國民保健署|英國國民保健署]]當了四年的實驗室助理<ref>{{cite web |first1=Frank |last1=Sanderson |first2=Clare |last2=Doran |title=Bernard Hogan-Howe |url=http://www.ljmu.ac.uk/Graduation/114807.htm |publisher=[[Liverpool_John_Moores_University|Liverpool John Moores University]] |accessdate=2011-09-12 |date=2010-07-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329114331/http://www.ljmu.ac.uk/Graduation/114807.htm |archivedate=2012-03-29 }}</ref>。

==警察生涯==
1979年，霍根-豪加入{{Link-en|南約克郡警察局|South Yorkshire Police}}，自此展開警察生涯，擔任過軍裝、刑事、交通及人事處人員<ref name='Police Roll of Honour'>{{cite web | url = http://www.policememorial.org.uk/index.php?mact=News,cntnt01,detail,0&cntnt01articleid=103&cntnt01returnid=62 | title = New Patrons | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archive-date = 2014-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417003731/http://www.policememorial.org.uk/index.php?mact=News,cntnt01,detail,0&cntnt01articleid=103&cntnt01returnid=62 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，後來擢升為[[唐卡斯特|唐卡斯特]]西區指揮官，由於在職期間極富進取心而獲上級選拔，於28歲時進入[[牛津大學墨頓學院|牛津大學墨頓學院]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Johnston |first=Philip |date=2011-09-13 |title=Bernard Hogan-Howe: a tough cop for a tough job at the Metropolitan Police |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/8759984/Bernard-Hogan-Howe-a-tough-cop-for-a-tough-job-at-the-Metropolitan-Police.html |newspaper=[[每日電訊報|Daily Telegraph]] |location=London |accessdate=2011-09-13 |archive-date=2011-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110914091211/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/8759984/Bernard-Hogan-Howe-a-tough-cop-for-a-tough-job-at-the-Metropolitan-Police.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>攻讀法律碩士學位<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sands |first1=Sarah |last2=Davenport |first2=Justin |date=2011-09-15 |title=Bernard Hogan-Howe: Dixon of Dock Green is my role model... police officers are not social workers |url=http://www.standard.co.uk/news/bernard-hoganhowe-dixon-of-dock-green-is-my-role-model-police-officers-are-not-social-workers-6443739.html |newspaper={{Link-en|倫敦標準晚報|London Evening Standard|London Evening Standard}} |accessdate=2014-03-05 |archive-date=2014-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306042958/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/bernard-hoganhowe-dixon-of-dock-green-is-my-role-model-police-officers-are-not-social-workers-6443739.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後又分別獲得[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]應用犯罪學[[深造文憑|深造文憑]]及[[雪菲爾大學|雪菲爾大學]][[工商管理碩士|工商管理碩士]]學位<ref name="四人">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14181898 |title=Who might be next Met Police commissioner? |publisher=BBC News |date=18 July 2011 |accessdate=2011-07-18 |archive-date=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718175326/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14181898 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://emba.group.shef.ac.uk/case-studies/case-study-bernard-hogan-howe |title=The Sheffield Executive MBA: Case study: Bernard Hogan-Howe |publisher=[[雪菲爾大學|University of Sheffield]] |accessdate=2011-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110618033621/http://emba.group.shef.ac.uk/case-studies/case-study-bernard-hogan-howe |archivedate=2011-06-18 }}</ref>。

1997年，霍根-豪調至{{Link-en|默西賽德郡警察局|Merseyside Police}}擔任社區事務{{Link-en|助理局長 (英國警察)|Assistant Chief Constable|助理局長}}，1999年改任地區行動助理局長。2001年後，霍根-豪調職到[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]擔任[[人力資源|人力資源]]{{Link-en|倫敦警察廳助理總監|Assistant Commissioner of Police of the Metropolis|助理總監}}，直至2004年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mpa.gov.uk/news/press/2001/01-022.htm |title=MPA appoints two Assistant Commissioners: DAC Tarique Ghaffur and ACC Bernard Hogan-Howe |accessdate=2008-03-10 |publisher=[[首都警察監管局|Metropolitan Police Authority]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080401034028/http://www.mpa.gov.uk/news/press/2001/01-022.htm |archivedate=2008-04-01 }}</ref>，2005年至2009年間又重返默西賽德警局、上任局長<ref name="gunthugs">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/merseyside/6396229.stm |title='Evict gun thugs' families' call |accessdate=10 March 2008 |publisher=BBC News |date=26 February 2007 |archive-date=2007-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070308161932/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/merseyside/6396229.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.merseyside.police.uk/index.aspx?articleid=3857|title=Temporary Chief Constable takes up the baton|accessdate=2009-11-01|publisher={{Link-en|默西賽德郡警局|Merseyside Police|Merseyside Police}}|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716055646/http://www.merseyside.police.uk/index.aspx?articleid=3857|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在任內對集團犯罪及持槍犯罪施展了嚴厲措施，致使當地的罪案率大幅度下降了40%<ref name="承諾打擊犯罪">{{Cite web |url=http://inspectorates.homeoffice.gov.uk/hmic/about/hm-inspectors.html |title=倫敦警察局新任局長承諾打擊犯罪 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]中文網 |date=2011-09-12 |accessdate=2014-09-29 |archive-date=2009-09-07 |archive-url=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20090907072226/http%3A//inspectorates.homeoffice.gov.uk/hmic/about/hm%2Dinspectors.html/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2009年至2011年間，他轉赴{{Link-en|女王陛下警務監督局|Her Majesty's Inspectorate of Constabulary|女皇警務監督局}}擔任監督官<ref>{{cite web |url=http://inspectorates.homeoffice.gov.uk/hmic/about/hm-inspectors.html |title=Her Majesty's Inspectors of Constabulary |accessdate=2009-11-01 |publisher={{Link-en|英國警務監督局|Her Majesty's Inspectorate of Constabulary|Her Majesty's Inspectorate of Constabulary}} |archive-date=2009-09-07 |archive-url=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20090907072226/http%3A//inspectorates.homeoffice.gov.uk/hmic/about/hm%2Dinspectors.html/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2011年7月17日，時任倫敦警察{{Link-en|倫敦警察廳總監|Commissioner of Police of the Metropolis|總監}}{{Link-en|保羅·史蒂文生 (英國警官)|Paul Stephenson (police officer)|保羅·史蒂文生}}因為警方在[[世界新聞報電話竊聽醜聞|世界新聞報電話竊聽案]]中涉入醜聞，而引咎辭職。當時的霍根-豪正身為警察廳助理總監、主管專業標準事務，而他在此後與另外3名高階警官——倫敦警察廳臨時總監{{Link-en|提姆·戈德溫|Tim Godwin}}、前{{Link-en|北愛爾蘭警察廳|Police Service of Northern Ireland}}總長{{Link-en|休·奥德|Hugh Orde}}和{{Link-en|斯克萊德警察局|Strathclyde Police}}局長{{Link-en|史蒂芬·豪斯|Stephen House}}一起競奪下屆的總監職位<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://world.time.com/2011/09/12/londons-new-police-chief-more-of-the-same/ |title=London’s New Police Chief: More of the Same? |publisher=[[時代雜誌|Time]] |date=2011-09-12 |accessdate=2014-09-29 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007062550/http://world.time.com/2011/09/12/londons-new-police-chief-more-of-the-same/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月12日，英政府宣布霍根-豪勝出<ref name="承諾打擊犯罪"></ref>、將於9月26日上任為倫敦警察廳新任總監<ref name="appointment" />。此前，霍根-豪所屬的專業標準-{zh-cn:处; zh-tw:處; zh-hk:科;}-（{{lang|en|Department of Professional Standards}}）曾打算要利用《{{Link-en|英國公務機密法|Official Secrets Act|公務機密法}}》向《[[衛報|衛報]]》施壓、要其公開世界新聞報竊聽案的相關信息來源，但此決定卻因為霍根-豪晉升為倫敦警察廳首長，而在他上任的五天前就遭到推翻<ref>{{cite news |last=Freedland |first=Jonathan Jonathan Freedland |title=The new Met chief's U-turn is welcome – he had made a gross misjudgment |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/sep/20/new-met-chief-u-turn-misjudgment |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |location=London |date=2009-09-21 |accessdate=2014-03-05 |archive-date=2012-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113011958/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/sep/20/new-met-chief-u-turn-misjudgment |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在霍根-豪任內，倫敦警察廳於2012在2月8日新創了[[警力|警力]]達1,000名的{{Link-en|三叉戟團伙犯罪指揮中心|Trident Gang Crime Command}}，負責應對倫敦的犯罪組織相關案件及暴力活動，亦處理了倫敦境內槍擊事件的防範和調查<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://content.met.police.uk/Article/History-of-Trident/1400014986671/gangcrime|title=History of Trident|publisher=Metropolitan Police Service|date=2013|accessdate=2014-09-29|archive-date=2014-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908035942/http://content.met.police.uk/Article/History-of-Trident/1400014986671/gangcrime|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/ukchina/simp/uk_life/2012/02/120209_life_gangs.shtml |title=倫敦警方重拳打擊團伙犯罪 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]中文網 |date=2012-02-09 |accessdate=2014-09-29 |archive-date=2012-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302091535/http://www.bbc.co.uk/ukchina/simp/uk_life/2012/02/120209_life_gangs.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年11月，霍根-豪與休·奥德和史蒂芬·豪斯一起成為全國性慈善組織——警察榮譽榜信託（{{lang|en|Police Roll of Honour Trust}}）的聯名贊助人<ref name='Police Roll of Honour'></ref>。

